title: 820-2567 no battery
message:
It wont recognize the battery in any way.
What should I check?

title: 820-2567 no battery
message: Check if there is room in your trash bin and get a $30 working board on Ebay. Bad SMC or ISL or both, these are not worth fixing. Once you have the board sorted you will probably find that the keyboard is bad too if this was liquid.
